        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6082e0dcabf4441653d1db00549cc54f?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
                "account_id": 168275,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 393632,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/393632/ezku",
                "reputation": 622,
                "display_name": "Ezku"
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 2.5",
            "score": 2,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1279715491,
            "creation_date": 1279715491,
            "body": "<p>The last word would be the non-space characters preceding the end or the string. You can define a set of characters with [] and negate that with a ^, as in [^a-z] to match everything but a-z.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>\"John Doe Jr\".replaceAll(\"([^ ]+)$\", \"&lt;strong&gt;$1&lt;/strong&gt;\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>This also has the advantage that it doesn't require that there be any spaces in the string, unlike Marcelo Cantos' answer.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 3299197,
            "question_id": 3299101
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/33fa45af0983107b1445c604ef60a0ed?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
                "account_id": 108817,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 288671,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/288671/vitalii-fedorenko",
                "reputation": 115090,
                "display_name": "Vitalii Fedorenko"
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 2.5",
            "score": 2,
            "is_accepted": true,
            "last_activity_date": 1279720408,
            "creation_date": 1279715620,
            "body": "<pre><code>\"John Doe Jr\".replaceAll(\"(\\\\S+)$\", \"&lt;strong&gt;$1&lt;/strong&gt;\")\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://java.sun.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/regex/Pattern.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">\\S<\/a> is a non-whitespace character<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 3299214,
            "question_id": 3299101,
            "last_edit_date": 1279720408
        }
